  "description": {
    "main": "This all-in-one Sony HT-S2000 sound bar captures the magic of the cinema. Dolby Atmos and DTS Virtual:X create a 3D soundscape, putting you smack dab in the middle of the action. Pop on a blockbuster, and you'll experience the full force of a jet overhead or tank firing. The upmixer adds a 3D audio twist to your stereo content and breathes fresh life into classics. Count on the centre speaker for crisp speech, and let the built-in dual sub awaken the bass. You won't miss a moment when the action moves from glass rattling booms to quiet whispers.",
    "goodToKnow": [
      "It's just as good at playing music too - you can stream over Bluetooth or plug in a USB stick",
      "Setup is simple but Sony's Home Entertainment Connect app is on hand to help if you need it",
      "It's designed to work perfectly in sync with Sony's wireless rear speakers and BRAVIA TVs (both sold separately)"
    ]
  },
